ble\n\n### Milestone 4 — Operational Reliability\nStatus: pending\n\nTargets:\n- background continue observability\n- clear loop status semantics\n- degraded-state handling\n- linked-vs-running distinction across surfaces\n\n### Milestone 5 — Publishable Product Quality\nStatus: pending\n\nTargets:\n- release workflow\n- screenshots / notes / docs\n- smoke validation routine\n- repo structure clarity\n\n## Slice Rules\n- Each tick completes one bounded, verifiable slice only.\n- Always validate syntax and package builds after code changes.\n- Always sync export repo changes back to the mirror workspace when behavior changes.\n- Always append an evolution note in `.claude/plans/loloop/`.\n- Update this active plan when milestone focus changes.\n\n## Immediate Next Slice Queue\n1. Drag/drop indicator clearing and board-boundary reliability pass\n2. T / S / M / L density normalization pass\n3. Needs Human occupancy and collapse behavior pass\n4. Board interaction polish and guardrails pass\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
